@startuml
title Quantum-Classical Simulation Loop

start
:Choose molecular problem;
:Build simplified Hamiltonian;
:Choose parameterized trial state;

repeat
  :Prepare quantum state;
  :Measure energy terms;
  :Send measurements to classical optimizer;
  :Update parameters;
repeat while (energy still improving?)

:Return estimated low-energy state;
stop

note right
  This is VQE intuition.
  It is not a promise that quantum
  computers solve all chemistry.
end note

@enduml

